data.description:
Private retreat with stunning views overlooking Siletz Bay and Salishan spit. Watch the sunset fron the perfect location, inside through a wall of windows, or outside on 2 decks on 2 levels.
Private driveway leads to home nestled on the hillside, detached garage and tranquil setting. Primary ensuite on main level, heated tile floors in great-room, 2nd bedroom, full bath and large loft upstairs (could convert to 3rd bedroom).  Enjoy the covered patio and hot tub , gardening, and did I mention the view??
